2. Then output ONLY the constraint program in a single ```python ...``` block.
    - Do NOT output any text after the python code block.
    - Do NOT repeat the class definitions.
    - Do NOT re-initialize the provided assets.
    - Do NOT overwrite asset variables; reference exactly the provided variable names/ids.
    - Add brief comments in code when helpful.
3. All constraint function calls MUST explicitly specify ALL parameters, including those with default values.
4. Do NOT use loops (for/while/etc.) in the constraint program.
5. Do NOT define helper variables/constants EXCEPT for:
